  "elapsed_s": 428.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a 5-- like a $5.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is a 5-something gold coin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And really, what's wonderful for me is that I have two mementos from that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One is a cigarette case that my mother gave to my father when they became engaged.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other is a pair of earrings that belonged to my grandmother, my father's mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to that same Czech man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think he was concerned because there were, like-- the Ukrainians or the Poles or everybody was all over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think we hid out in some straw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother said that she-- we hid out in some hay or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't go back to the attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she would give him money for us that-- she would give him money so he could buy food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and that's where we remained for a while, there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
